MENU_PKG_QT
  Here you'll find options for Qt.

SDECFG_PKG_QT_PREFIX
  Please enter the prefix where you want Qt installed.

SDECFG_PKG_QT_EXCEPTION
  Whether to enable support for exceptions.

SDECFG_PKG_QT_STL
  Whether to enable support for STL data types.
